# Network Configuration

## Sepolia Testnet (Recommended for Testing)
SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=https://sepolia.infura.io/v3/YOUR_INFURA_KEY
PRIVATE_KEY=0xYourPrivateKeyHere

## Optional: Etherscan API Key (For Contract Verification)
ETHERSCAN_API_KEY=YOUR_ETHERSCAN_API_KEY

## Optional: Alchemy RPC (Alternative to Infura)
ALCHEMY_API_KEY=YOUR_ALCHEMY_API_KEY

## Optional: Custom RPC URLs
LOCALHOST_RPC_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8545

## Optional: Hardhat Network Configuration
HARDHAT_NETWORK=hardhat

# Note: Never commit this file with real private keys to version control!
# Always use .env for local secrets and .env.example for templates
